title: 100% Transparency
description:
Sadie interviews Olympic gold medalist Shawn Johnson and her husband and former NFL player, Andrew East. Join them as they discuss how they learned to cultivate 100% transparency in their marriage and on social media, their story of falling in love, and why they keep their relationship full of laughter!
